{% from "components/vital-sign-body-fat-as-percentage-view/macro.njk" import vitalSignBodyFatAsPercentageView %}

<h2>Default</h2>
<p>{{ vitalSignBodyFatAsPercentageView({
  value: "22.5",
  label: "Body fat"
}) }}</p>

<h2>Accessibility</h2>
<p>Because the "%" symbol is widely understood by screen readers,
  the unit is rendered in a plain
  <code>&lt;span class="vital-sign-unit"&gt;%&lt;/span&gt;</code>
  rather than an <code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code>. Set
  <code>params.label</code> to clarify the reading's purpose in
  contexts where the percent alone is ambiguous.</p>
